1.title: Episode #1.1

episode of.title: Star Wars: The Idiotic Clone Trooper (TV Series 2014– )

1.plot: Spectated by Master Plo Koon and Master Kit Fisto, there is a birth of just another ordinary clone trooper. Or is it? Master Plo Koon and Kit Fisto found that there was something odd about the soldier during it's birth. And guess what? They were right. Watch as Plo Koon and Kit Fisto have to put up with all the dumb crap that The Idiotic Clone Trooper ends up doing in his first exciting days of life.

2.title: Episode #1.2

episode of.title: Star Wars: The Idiotic Clone Trooper (TV Series 2014– )

2.plot: The Idiotic Clone Trooper is found unconscious by a squadron of clone troopers who were sent to find and train him for combat. The chaos begins as soon as he regains consciousness and begins to be a complete derp. Watch as Commander Cody fails to train The Idiotic Clone Trooper to the point that he is driven crazy and gives up completely.

3.title: Episode #1.3

episode of.title: Star Wars: The Idiotic Clone Trooper (TV Series 2014– )

3.plot: The Idiotic Clone Trooper is forced to go to school because clearly Plo Koon and Kit Fisto haven't learned yet that he cannot be taught to do anything in succession. Watch as The Idiotic Clone Trooper and some other people cause tons of chaos and drive their Special Needs Teacher insane to the point that somehow other official-ey and government-ey people get involved.

4.title: Episode #1.4

episode of.title: Star Wars: The Idiotic Clone Trooper (TV Series 2014– )

4.plot: Once upon a time there was a clone. That now, since he was too chaotic to be held in the hands of the republic's clone army, is living his life like a normal civilian in the galaxy. Unfortunate for Kit Fisto and Plo Koon that they are still in charge of making sure he doesn't accidentally become the galactic emperor by killing nearly everyone in the galaxy, watch as The Retarded Clone Trooper goes through a basic, normal day at home in his life.

5.title: Episode #1.5

episode of.title: Star Wars: The Idiotic Clone Trooper (TV Series 2014– )

5.plot: When The Retarded Clone Trooper decides to go to a bar, what happens? A pile of rubble. Watch as The Retarded Clone Trooper meets a new rival and completely demolishes an innocent bar out of his idiotically charged anger.

6.title: Episode #1.6

episode of.title: Star Wars: The Idiotic Clone Trooper (TV Series 2014– )

6.plot: When The Retarded Clone Trooper decides to casually waltz into The Emperor's Throne Room, he accidentally saves the galaxy from all future problems that Emperor Palpatine would have caused. After failing to even finish his supposedly persuasive speech to turn The Retarded Clone Trooper to the dark side, Emperor Palpatine commands Darth Vader to kill The Retarded Clone Trooper, which Vader failed to do, leading to their very quick deaths. Watch as The Retarded Clone Trooper kills the 2 most powerful Sith Lords in the galaxy in the less than 2 minutes that he has to do ...

7.title: Episode #1.7

episode of.title: Star Wars: The Idiotic Clone Trooper (TV Series 2014– )

7.plot: After The Sexy Clone Trooper builds his own big, expensive underground base, his first decision is to send his thug out to kidnap The Retarded Clone Trooper and friends. After tying them together and locking them in a door-less and windowless room The Sexy Clone Trooper greets his rival and explains what he did, and leaves, not expecting anything against his plans to happen. But of course, EVERYTHING against his plans happens. Watch as The Retarded Clone Trooper demolishes all The Sexy Clone Trooper's brand-new goodies and fights him yet again.

imdb.plot outline: When what seemingly was the birth of just another ordinary clone trooper occurs, Plo Koon and Kit Fisto realize their horribly false observations. The Idioitc Clone Trooper springs to life and starts a never-ending conflict that the Jedi Masters are forced by the Jedi Counsel during The Clone Wars era to take on, for they are guardians of peace and justice, so it is simply their job to contain this clone.
